<i>adjective</i>: 일목요연하다 [일모교연하다], 명쾌하다 [명쾌하다], 명징하다 [명징하다], 똑똑하다 [똑또카다] <i>determiner</i>: 명시적 [명시적] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>일목요연하다 [일모교연하다]</dt><br>
<dd>clear-cut; explicit; understandable</dd><br>
<dd>한눈에 알 수 있을 만큼 분명하고 뚜렷하다.</dd><br>
<dd>So clear and simple as to be understood at a glance.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>명쾌하다 [명쾌하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. clear; explicit; lucid</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 글이 앞뒤가 들어맞고 체계가 있어 시원스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>A speech or writing's being straightforward due to its coherent and organized structure.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cheerful; blithe; jovial</dd><br>
<dd>명랑하고 쾌활하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being gay, cheerful and outgoing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>명징하다 [명징하다]</dt><br>
<dd>clear; explicit</dd><br>
<dd>아주 분명하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Very clear.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>똑똑하다 [똑또카다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. definite; explicit; well-defined</dd><br>
<dd>분명하고 확실하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Clear and distinct.</dd><br>
<dd>2. clever; bright; sensible</dd><br>
<dd>머리가 좋고 영리하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Intelligent and wise.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>determiner</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>명시적 [명시적]</dt><br>
<dd>explicit; clear</dd><br>
<dd>내용이나 뜻을 분명하게 드러내 보이는.</dd><br>
<dd>Being clear in a statement or an expression.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>